# Windows specific commands
nvm install 14.17.3
nvm use 14.17.3
npm i -g pnpm
pnpm init
pnpm i --save-dev @types/node@^14
pnpm i --save-dev typescript
pnpm i --save-dev ts-node
pnpm i --save-dev nodemon
pnpx tsc --init

Create .gitignore based on
https://www.toptal.com/developers/gitignore/api/node

Create src folder to store the code

Create public

Edit package.json:
